#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/funqy-amazon-lambda.adoc:299
msgid "The are times where you may have to add additional entries to the `function.zip` lambda deployment that is generated by the build.  To do this create a `zip.jvm` or `zip.native` directory within `src/main`.  Create `zip.jvm/` if you are doing a pure Java.  `zip.native/` if you are doing a native deployment."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/funqy-amazon-lambda.adoc:301
msgid "Any you files and directories you create under your zip directory will be included within `function.zip`"
